---
title: Mastodon instance
author: hannes
abstract: Mastodon is a federated social network with microblogging features.  Would be great to run our own instance as MirageOS unikernel.
tags: help needed, active project, http, social
---

[Mastodon](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mastodon_(software)) is a federated social network with microblogging features.

An overview of what we need to implement is [Specs and RFC used](https://github.com/tootsuite/documentation/blob/master/Specs-and-RFCs-used.md).
Please contact mirageos-devel@lists.xenproject.org if you'd like to start this project.